WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:04.070
Good evening, everybody. Thank you

00:00:04.080 --> 00:00:06.630
for joining us again tonight. I

00:00:06.630 --> 00:00:06.640
have

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:08.070
my sweetheart with me tonight. I told

00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:10.629
her we will go ahead and

00:00:10.639 --> 00:00:13.990
pray and seek the Lord to see

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.950
what He has for us tonight

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:20.950
concerning our nation. Today,

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:23.429
when I was driving around and

00:00:23.439 --> 00:00:24.950
doing errands,

00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:28.310
I saw in the spirit

00:00:28.320 --> 00:00:30.870
a headline in the New

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:33.670
York Times.

00:00:33.680 --> 00:00:36.709
The caption in

00:00:36.719 --> 00:00:40.310
bold letters said, 'Terror in

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:47.029
Manhattan.'Thank

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:53.670
you, son. 'Terror

00:00:53.670 --> 00:00:53.680
in Manhattan.'In

00:00:53.680 --> 00:00:56.310
the picture,

00:00:56.320 --> 00:01:01.029
I saw a lot of smoke and

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:03.029
a building.

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:04.950
I saw

00:01:04.960 --> 00:01:08.070
'Terror in

00:01:08.070 --> 00:01:08.080
Manhattan'in

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:12.149
bold

00:01:12.159 --> 00:01:17.749
on the front of this newspaper,

00:01:17.749 --> 00:01:17.759
and

00:01:17.759 --> 00:01:19.990
below it,

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:24.149
'Terror strikes again in

00:01:24.159 --> 00:01:27.830
America.'Then

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:30.149
it had the article

00:01:30.159 --> 00:01:33.350
of what happened. As I was

00:01:33.350 --> 00:01:33.360
praying—I

00:01:33.360 --> 00:01:36.230
guess we're

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:38.390
just going to jump right into this

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:43.270
to save you

00:01:43.270 --> 00:01:43.280
time—I

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:47.030
saw an umbrella with beautiful colors; it was a protection.

00:01:47.030 --> 00:01:47.040
But because of choices that were made,

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:49.350
this umbrella

00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:04.230
had holes all in it.

00:02:04.240 --> 00:02:07.190
Decisions

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:09.990
being made

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:13.190
over the years caused the holes to get bigger and

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:16.070
bigger. The more the

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:19.110
umbrella was covering over America, the

00:02:19.110 --> 00:02:19.120
more

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:20.630
people were holding it and

00:02:20.640 --> 00:02:21.990
were excited to have it because it

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:25.190
blocked the storms and

00:02:25.190 --> 00:02:25.200
the

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:28.550
plan of the enemy. This

00:02:28.560 --> 00:02:31.830
umbrella was a covering.

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:35.750
As American citizens or

00:02:35.750 --> 00:02:35.760
people

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:37.830
around the world, you have this prayer

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:40.309
covering from the

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:43.350
churches. But as you

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:45.910
make decisions against God's

00:02:45.920 --> 00:02:48.550
word, against God's plan, and against what

00:02:48.560 --> 00:02:52.309
God originally wanted for us, you

00:02:52.309 --> 00:02:52.319
cause

00:02:52.319 --> 00:02:55.589
holes in your umbrella.

00:02:55.599 --> 00:02:57.270
We repent, and the

00:02:57.270 --> 00:02:57.280
covering is

00:02:57.280 --> 00:02:59.589
still there,

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:02.869
but there were holes in it because of

00:03:02.869 --> 00:03:02.879
those

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:04.949
decisions.

00:03:04.959 --> 00:03:07.750
I saw these holes

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:09.910
that were seemingly really small at the

00:03:09.920 --> 00:03:13.110
beginning, like pinholes,

00:03:13.110 --> 00:03:13.120
but

00:03:13.120 --> 00:03:15.509
over the course of time,

00:03:15.519 --> 00:03:18.710
the holes got larger and

00:03:18.720 --> 00:03:21.350
larger

00:03:21.360 --> 00:03:24.229
until

00:03:24.239 --> 00:03:28.710
the umbrella was no longer there.

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:30.949
The Lord showed me the prayer

00:03:30.959 --> 00:03:33.750
covering of a home

00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:35.910
and the importance of the

00:03:35.920 --> 00:03:38.470
male being the head of the

00:03:38.480 --> 00:03:42.470
household.

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:44.789
The man brings a covering over

00:03:44.799 --> 00:03:46.710
it, and the wife provides a prayer

00:03:46.720 --> 00:03:49.990
covering, too. There is so

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:52.470
much importance in a man leading his

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:55.190
family. The Lord was showing me the

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:58.630
importance of righteous men in the

00:03:58.640 --> 00:04:01.589
household rising up and being what God

00:04:01.589 --> 00:04:01.599
has

00:04:01.599 --> 00:04:03.350
called you to be: lead

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:06.070
your family, take them to church, pray

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:08.710
with your kids, and pray with your wife. Be

00:04:08.720 --> 00:04:11.990
a godly spouse. Speak good things

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:13.830
over your children

00:04:13.830 --> 00:04:13.840
and

00:04:13.840 --> 00:04:15.990
your wife. Bless your children

00:04:15.990 --> 00:04:16.000
and

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:18.550
your wife

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:20.310
spiritually, physically, and financially.

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:24.710
Whatever you can do, you be that head.

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:29.350
I saw that as America goes, as

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:31.749
the church goes, and as big decisions

00:04:31.749 --> 00:04:31.759
go,

00:04:31.759 --> 00:04:34.230
that

00:04:34.230 --> 00:04:34.240
covering—no

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:37.270
matter how much we prayed and

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:40.310
asked God to cover things—the more

00:04:40.310 --> 00:04:40.320
unbiblical

00:04:40.320 --> 00:04:43.030
decisions were made, like those made

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:46.150
in New York by

00:04:46.150 --> 00:04:46.160
the

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:49.110
mayor, the more

00:04:49.110 --> 00:04:49.120
it

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:51.270
caused

00:04:51.280 --> 00:04:55.830
holes.

00:04:55.840 --> 00:04:59.670
I saw a terror attack, and the Lord

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:01.510
said, 'Do you see the power of prayer,

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:03.990
Brandon? What it does? It brings that

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:06.070
covering. But because you make

00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:08.070
unrighteous decisions, you open the door

00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:09.830
for the enemy.'I said, 'Lord, I

00:05:09.840 --> 00:05:11.749
need

00:05:11.759 --> 00:05:15.510
scriptures.'He

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:18.710
brought up Job

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:20.870
and other scriptures

00:05:20.870 --> 00:05:20.880
that

00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:24.629
Diana wrote down.

00:05:24.639 --> 00:05:29.830
The devil said,

00:05:29.840 --> 00:05:33.189
'You've put a hedge around Job

00:05:33.199 --> 00:05:35.029
and I'm not able to touch it,'but if you

00:05:35.039 --> 00:05:37.189
remove that

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:39.909
hedge,

00:05:39.919 --> 00:05:43.350
what Job feared the most came on him. He

00:05:43.360 --> 00:05:46.070
opened the door through fear;

00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:49.749
fear tolerated, faith contaminated.

00:05:49.759 --> 00:05:52.310
As he was making sacrifices out of

00:05:52.320 --> 00:05:54.230
fear for his children

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:56.150
and acting out

00:05:56.160 --> 00:05:57.830
of fear, he opened the door for

00:05:57.840 --> 00:06:00.230
it.

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:02.550
Now,

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:04.870
when we have a church

00:06:04.880 --> 00:06:06.390
covering and you keep praying over it,

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:09.590
He showed me the

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:11.590
thorns.

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:16.390
Not Hosea, I believe it was in

00:06:16.400 --> 00:06:21.029
Ezekiel—whoever

00:06:21.039 --> 00:06:23.110
breaks a hedge, the serpent

00:06:23.120 --> 00:06:25.110
will bite him. Okay, that's

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:29.749
Ecclesiastes 10:8: 'Whoever breaks a

00:06:29.759 --> 00:06:34.070
hedge, a serpent will bite

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:36.629
him.'As

00:06:38.639 --> 00:06:42.469
you break the hedge

00:06:42.469 --> 00:06:42.479
and

00:06:42.479 --> 00:06:44.710
that umbrella of

00:06:44.720 --> 00:06:46.870
covering, it

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:48.710
allows the enemy to come in and kill,

00:06:48.720 --> 00:06:51.110
steal, and destroy. We have authority,

00:06:51.120 --> 00:06:53.110
but if you keep

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:55.990
making ungodly decisions, and He says,

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:57.590
'I want you to live

00:06:59.110 --> 00:06:59.120
righteously,'but

00:07:03.270 --> 00:07:03.280
you

00:07:05.039 --> 00:07:07.270
are

00:07:09.440 --> 00:07:10.870
sleeping around while

00:07:10.870 --> 00:07:10.880
claiming

00:07:10.880 --> 00:07:13.029
to

00:07:13.029 --> 00:07:13.039
be

00:07:13.039 --> 00:07:14.629
a

00:07:14.629 --> 00:07:14.639
praying

00:07:14.639 --> 00:07:16.950
Christian,

00:07:16.950 --> 00:07:16.960
you

00:07:16.960 --> 00:07:18.150
are

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:20.950
opening the door. That

00:07:20.960 --> 00:07:22.710
covering

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:25.990
gets holes in it because you are allowing

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:29.670
sin in. That

00:07:29.670 --> 00:07:29.680
is

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:31.110
what the Lord was showing me

00:07:31.120 --> 00:07:34.870
today: the covering of

00:07:34.880 --> 00:07:37.350
prayer over America as we keep making

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:39.589
these bad decisions.

00:07:39.599 --> 00:07:40.870
That's what He keeps talking about in

00:07:40.870 --> 00:07:40.880
1

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:44.150
Corinthians 5:5. It

00:07:44.150 --> 00:07:44.160
is

00:07:44.160 --> 00:07:46.230
not His will for any of us

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:47.909
to perish. Ladies and gentlemen, you

00:07:47.919 --> 00:07:50.469
think because you go through a hard time

00:07:50.479 --> 00:07:53.670
for a season, that is God's judgment.

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:56.390
True judgment is separation from God

00:07:56.400 --> 00:07:58.550
for eternity.

00:07:58.560 --> 00:08:02.230
It's not the day-to-day

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:08.469
hard

00:08:08.469 --> 00:08:08.479
times.

00:08:08.479 --> 00:08:10.390
The way the Lord kept

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:12.230
showing me was, 'That is not judgment,

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:15.510
Brandon. True judgment is whenever you

00:08:15.520 --> 00:08:17.749
are going to hell forever and there is no

00:08:17.759 --> 00:08:21.510
returning. It's

00:08:21.520 --> 00:08:24.230
the point where there is no turning

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:26.550
back; you are in hell

00:08:26.550 --> 00:08:26.560
forever.'The

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:29.029
moment you take your last breath and you do

00:08:29.029 --> 00:08:29.039
not

00:08:29.039 --> 00:08:31.029
have Jesus Christ as your Lord and

00:08:31.039 --> 00:08:33.430
personal Savior, if you are not a

00:08:33.430 --> 00:08:33.440
born-again

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:35.670
Christian, that

00:08:35.670 --> 00:08:35.680
is

00:08:35.680 --> 00:08:39.350
true judgment.

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:43.509
But having a shaking to awaken

00:08:43.509 --> 00:08:43.519
people—like

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:45.590
what I

00:08:45.590 --> 00:08:45.600
have

00:08:45.600 --> 00:08:47.350
seen coming—they will all say,

00:08:47.360 --> 00:08:49.430
'This is judgment. God's mad,'and they will call it an Ichabod. 'God

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:51.670
has

00:08:51.680 --> 00:08:53.910
departed from America.'No,

00:08:53.910 --> 00:08:53.920
it is

00:08:53.920 --> 00:08:56.710
people making poor

00:08:56.710 --> 00:08:56.720
choices and

00:08:56.720 --> 00:08:59.190
voting

00:08:59.190 --> 00:08:59.200
unwisely.

00:08:59.200 --> 00:09:01.350
They keep thinking

00:09:01.350 --> 00:09:01.360
they

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:03.190
can do these

00:09:03.190 --> 00:09:03.200
things without

00:09:03.200 --> 00:09:07.110
repercussions. I

00:09:07.110 --> 00:09:07.120
am

00:09:07.120 --> 00:09:09.829
trying to tell you what I

00:09:09.839 --> 00:09:11.350
keep seeing. When I saw the

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:15.110
headlines in the paper,

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:17.190
I said, 'Oh

00:09:17.190 --> 00:09:17.200
Lord.'He

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:19.829
said, 'Brandon, do you

00:09:19.839 --> 00:09:22.949
see the importance of a choice?

00:09:22.959 --> 00:09:24.870
Do you see the importance of

00:09:24.880 --> 00:09:26.470
the prayer covering that you

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:28.470
bring over your

00:09:28.470 --> 00:09:28.480
family?'That

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:32.310
covers you;

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:34.310
you have the authority to pray that your

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:36.230
family is always in the right

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:37.910
place at the right time. But I am talking

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:40.310
about as a city as a whole. You keep making poor

00:09:40.310 --> 00:09:40.320
choices and

00:09:40.320 --> 00:09:42.949
voting

00:09:42.949 --> 00:09:42.959
in

00:09:42.959 --> 00:09:46.230
ways that allow the enemy to get

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:48.790
a stronghold in an area. That is why

00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:50.230
I was praying over these things today.

00:09:50.240 --> 00:09:51.670
People might say,

00:09:51.680 --> 00:09:53.750
'Brandon, you're being too harsh,'but

00:09:53.750 --> 00:09:53.760
I am

00:09:53.760 --> 00:09:54.870
just telling you what I am praying

00:09:54.880 --> 00:09:58.630
over today. It is a little raw,

00:09:58.640 --> 00:10:00.710
but this is what I am seeing

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:02.550
in the headlines. I saw a

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:07.269
great shaking coming again.

00:10:07.279 --> 00:10:09.829
I keep seeing these things, and

00:10:09.839 --> 00:10:11.350
quite frankly, it is very

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:13.670
sobering.

00:10:13.680 --> 00:10:17.509
I even told her, "I

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:19.990
could feel

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:22.790
such a shifting last night,"praying over President

00:10:22.800 --> 00:10:26.150
Trump and the things I saw.

00:10:26.160 --> 00:10:28.150
I'm going to go over some of that,

00:10:28.160 --> 00:10:30.069
but I was just trying to give you

00:10:30.069 --> 00:10:30.079
an update

00:10:30.079 --> 00:10:33.670
of what we saw

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:35.910
today as I'm praying. I want to go

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:39.750
over this. Remember yesterday,

00:10:39.760 --> 00:10:42.710
we saw a lot about drones

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:44.949
last night and the night before. We kept

00:10:44.959 --> 00:10:47.190
seeing drones in the

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:50.230
sky, and I saw a new wave of terror

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:53.670
activity in America using drones from

00:10:53.680 --> 00:10:57.190
Amazon strapped with explosive

00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:58.790
devices.

00:10:58.800 --> 00:11:00.150
I thought that was interesting

00:11:00.160 --> 00:11:01.990
because I never see that; I

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:05.110
always see them using

00:11:05.120 --> 00:11:08.550
vans, trucks, or semis, and the

00:11:08.560 --> 00:11:10.069
Lord keeps telling me to pray over this,

00:11:10.079 --> 00:11:13.590
but now I'm seeing drones more. As

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:15.829
I've been seeing all these

00:11:15.839 --> 00:11:17.750
things about drones and praying over

00:11:17.760 --> 00:11:20.069
New Year's Eve and the Macy's

00:11:20.079 --> 00:11:22.550
Thanksgiving Day Parade, Braden stumbled

00:11:22.560 --> 00:11:26.069
upon this. I'll let you watch this.

00:11:26.079 --> 00:11:28.150
This is not a coincidence; this is

00:11:28.160 --> 00:11:29.590
how we're being led on this

00:11:29.600 --> 00:11:31.190
channel. I think it's very

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:33.269
interesting what's being

00:11:33.279 --> 00:11:34.790
said. Do you have it ready? This

00:11:34.790 --> 00:11:34.800
is

00:11:34.800 --> 00:11:36.069
Fox News.

00:11:36.079 --> 00:11:38.870
It's

00:11:38.880 --> 00:11:41.030
not a coincidence what we've been

00:11:41.040 --> 00:11:42.550
hearing

00:11:42.560 --> 00:11:43.990
because they're talking about it, and

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:46.069
the Trump administration is already

00:11:46.079 --> 00:11:48.870
