00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:51.590
doing all the things they can to

00:11:51.600 --> 00:11:54.550
combat what they believe are credible

00:11:54.560 --> 00:11:57.030
threats. We're getting

00:11:57.040 --> 00:11:58.949
this by the spirit of God. This news

