listening to our webcast? Are

00:12:08.959 --> 00:12:12.949
these news reporters watching

00:12:12.949 --> 00:12:12.959
us?"I

00:12:12.959 --> 00:12:15.829
don't believe

00:12:15.839 --> 00:12:18.629
they are, but they could be.

00:12:18.629 --> 00:12:18.639
Wouldn't

00:12:18.639 --> 00:12:20.470
it be neat if Fox News was watching?

00:12:20.480 --> 00:12:23.350
Maybe they'll get saved if they're not.

00:12:23.360 --> 00:12:25.430
I think it's interesting that

00:12:25.440 --> 00:12:28.150
we are praying over these things and

00:12:28.160 --> 00:12:31.269
it's coming up in the news. This is

00:12:31.279 --> 00:12:33.990
exactly the assignment the

00:12:34.000 --> 00:12:35.829
