coming in, the Lord said this is

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:44.389
related to Ukraine

00:12:44.389 --> 00:12:44.399
and

00:12:44.399 --> 00:12:47.670
black swan events—major events

00:12:47.680 --> 00:12:53.190
to shake New York as we see the

